Citation.sTitle: Densities and Excess Molar Volumes for Acetone + Propionic Acid + Water from (283.15 to 323.15) K at Atmospheric Pressure
Citation.sAbstract: This paper presents experimental densities for the system acetone + propionic acid + water at atmospheric pressure from (283.15 to 323.15) K. A vibrating-tube densimeter provides density measurements over the entire composition range. We have calculated the excess volumes of the mixture and represent them with a Redlich-Kister-type polynomial.
